Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.22,OreimoDefault,Ayase,0000,0000,0000,,{Please go home.}Biến về nhà đi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.91,0:03:18.66,OreimoDefault,Ayase,0000,0000,0000,,{I want you out of here!}Em muốn anh rời khỏi đây!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.66,0:03:19.69,OreimoDefault,Kyousuke,0000,0000,0000,,{H-Hey!}N-Này!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.69,0:03:21.17,OreimoDefault,Ayase,0000,0000,0000,,{Get out of my sight, you liar!}Anh cút đi khỏi mắt em, đồ nói dối!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.17,0:03:23.88,OreimoDefault,Kyousuke,0000,0000,0000,,{What's that supposed to mean? When did I lie?!}Ý em là sao? Anh nói dối hồi nào?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.88,0:03:24.92,OreimoDefault,Ayase,0000,0000,0000,,{The whole time!}Mọi lúc!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.92,0:03:26.92,OreimoDefault,Ayase,0000,0000,0000,,{Everything you said was a lie!}Những gì anh nói ra đều là nói dối cả!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.40,0:03:29.17,OreimoDefault,Ayasemom,0000,0000,0000,,{Is something the matter, Ayase?}Có chuyện gì sao Ayase?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.05,0:03:32.43,OreimoDefault,Kyousuke,0000,0000,0000,,{Oh crap!}Tiêu rồi!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.69,0:03:46.19,OreimoDefault,Kanako,0000,0000,0000,,{Well, see you there, Ayase!}Rồi, gặp cậu tại đó, Ayase!
